title: United Kingdom Imports of Rubber & Related Articles
description: Imports of Rubber & Related Articles in the United Kingdom increased to 404.95 GBP Million in September from 374.99 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Rubber & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 274.42 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 530.70 GBP Million in October of 2020 and a record low of 110.73 GBP Million in December of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Rubber & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
